# Grama Niladhari Module - Wireframes
*Grama Niladhari Registration, Profile Management & Admin Verification System*

## 📋 Overview
This repository contains the complete wireframing documentation for the **Grama Niladhari (GN) Module** of the **Smart Grama Sewa** . Both low-fidelity and high-fidelity wireframes are included to showcase the design evolution from conceptual layouts to final polished interfaces.

The Grama Niladhari Module is designed to digitize and streamline the workflow of Grama Niladhari officers, enabling efficient citizen service management, administrative oversight, and community communication.

---

## 🎯 Module Objectives
- **GN Registration & Profile Management:** Streamlined onboarding and profile maintenance for Grama Niladhari officers
- **Request & Appointment Management:** Efficient handling of citizen requests and appointments
- **Community Communication:** Broadcast announcements, service updates, and urgent notices
- **Real-time Status Updates:** Dynamic availability tracking (Available / Busy / On Field)

